File::Navigate - Navigate freely inside a text file
===================================================

The module is a glorified wrapper for tell() and seek().

It aims to simplify the creation of logfile analysis tools by providing
a facility to jump around freely inside the contents of large files
without creating the need to slurp excessive amounts of data.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other modules and libraries. Tested on Perl 5.6.1.

